00:38:07.960 --> 00:38:12.430
So I've taken this same problem.

00:38:12.430 --> 00:38:17.160
There is the charge
oscillating up and down

00:38:17.160 --> 00:38:24.280
with amplitude z0
cosine omega t prime.

00:38:24.280 --> 00:38:30.980
And what we see-- well, we
